Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.76,0:00:04.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Fem un pas decidit cap un futur gloriós. Estem del tot mentalitzats!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:06.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'escenari d'avui són uns estudis de televisió.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:08.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,El perill no pot amagar la seva cara autèntica
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,en aquest món de màscares espectaculars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sempre descobreix l'única veritat! Sembla un nen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:16.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Seaside moon, seaside sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.24,0:00:23.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,itsumademo kawanaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:30.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,kokoro wo mou ichido kimi ni todoketai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,Glorious mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:40.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,So give me the reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:44.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,leave me here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,The reason why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:50.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:53.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,So must be the truth, baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:58.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,shall we end then it's up to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:02.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is a diferent day, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:05.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,And I know when I'm ready.
